```r
##all trimesters
hc_child_all <- 
  lmer(
    hc_trimlog ~ 
      seg_week + 
      sum_sev_child_cent + 
      weeks_preg_cent + 
      (seg_week|ID), 
    data = hcc
  )
summary(hc_child_all)
```
